 Ohio, Michigan &amp; Maryland. Get smart Congress</strong>. Also, the countries that send us cars have taken advantage of the U.S. for decades. The President has great power on this issue - <strong>Because of the G.M. event, it is being studied now!<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump&d=25Bn80kblrlf5eFaRga00p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b3f8cc12\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump</a>"},{"pid":"5a73296723d4d88acb1fbf13fac6fb6b0ec35266","tid":920883,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43eed9f764baeefc4264587094b04590087b86a4","tid":920883,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9686ff160040079a7551f38ea0b20d3cf7b5ed9e","tid":920883,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246a5bf800980a9d9b0ebe68560223d4671635c9","tid":920883,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"加到400000%又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國人幾折墮都唔使買支那車啦。何況D日本同歐洲車咁平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"佢呢招似係JER通用個D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於中國D車廠真係表示關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"美國就算係窮人可能都要車代步<br />\n你寫包單一定無人買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"窮既咪買二手車囉，兩年車齡都係幾千美金，日本車咁耐用操十幾年冇問題啦。"}]}